{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775836331447,"sessionID":"ses_287eaa4dfffe6ByyA3ZuLglM2s","part":{"id":"prt_d78174f88001PDOgQO4QvEGAcI","messageID":"msg_d781739ca001mcfvOGuqjiXtdS","sessionID":"ses_287eaa4dfffe6ByyA3ZuLglM2s","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_ac6e3bf747bd4394b5ede92a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/store\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-014/design.md`, `changes/AR-014/proposal.md`, `delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 实现 Valkey 构造函数\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `store_valkey.go`，定义 `valkeyStore` 结构体\n- [ ] 1.2 实现 `newValkeyStore() (*valkeyStore, error)` 构造函数\n- [ ] 1.3 验证 `VALKEY_ADDR` 非空，否则返回 `errors.New(\"VALKEY_ADDR is required\")`\n- [ ] 1.4 验证 `VALKEY_PASSWORD`（除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`）\n- [ ] 1.5 使用 `valkey.NewClient` 创建客户端，ping 验证连接\n- [ ] 1.6 更新 `singleton.go` 中 `initStore()` 支持 `STORE_TYPE=valkey`\n- [ ] 1.7 新增构造函数单元测试 `TestNewValkeyStore_MissingAddr`\n- [ ] 1.8 新增构造函数单元测试 `TestNewValkeyStore_MissingPassword`\n- [ ] 1.9 新增构造函数单元测试 `TestNewValkeyStore_PasswordBypassed`\n\n**Verification:** `newValkeyStore` 签名返回 `(*valkeyStore, error)`；无 `klog.Fatal` 调用；singleton.go 正确处理 error；构造测试全绿\n\n---\n\n## T2. 实现 Valkey CRUD 操作\n\n- [ ] 2.1 实现 `sessionKey(sessionID string) string` 辅助方法\n- [ ] 2.2 实现 `Ping(ctx context.Context) error`\n- [ ] 2.3 实现 `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)` — 使用 GET，nil → ErrNotFound\n- [ ] 2.4 实现 `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` — 验证 nil/零 ExpiresAt，Pipeline: SET NX + ZADD expiry + ZADD activity\n- [ ] 2.5 实现 `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` — SET XX，key 不存在返回错误\n- [ ] 2.6 实现 `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)` — Pipeline: DEL + ZREM expiry + ZREM activity\n- [ ] 2.7 实现 `Close() error`\n- [ ] 2.8 运行 `go build ./pkg/store/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** 所有方法签名与 `Store` 接口一致；`go build` 零错误\n\n---\n\n## T3. 实现 Valkey 查询操作\n\n- [ ] 3.1 实现 `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs(ctx, sessionIDs)` — 使用 MGET 批量加载\n- [ ] 3.2 实现 `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` — ZRANGEBYSCORE + loadSandboxesBySessionIDs\n- [ ] 3.3 实现 `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` — ZRANGEBYSCORE + loadSandboxesBySessionIDs\n- [ ] 3.4 实现 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at)` — EXISTS 验证 + ZADD\n- [ ] 3.5 运行 `go build ./pkg/store/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** 方法签名与 design.md §3.1 一致；MGET 单次调用而非循环 GET\n\n---\n\n## T4. 编写 Valkey 单元测试\n\n- [ ] 4.1 创建 `store_valkey_test.go`\n- [ ] 4.2 实现测试辅助 `newTestValkeyStore(t)` 和 `testSandboxInfo(sessionID)`\n- [ ] 4.3 编写 Ping 测试（成功/失败）\n- [ ] 4.4 编写 GetSandboxBySessionID 测试（Found/NotFound）\n- [ ] 4.5 编写 StoreSandbox 测试（Success/NilRejected/ZeroExpiry/Idempotent）\n- [ ] 4.6 编写 UpdateSandbox 测试（Success/MissingKey）\n- [ ] 4.7 编写 DeleteSandboxBySessionID 测试\n- [ ] 4.8 编写 ListExpiredSandboxes 测试（正常/ZeroLimit/OrphanMember）\n- [ ] 4.9 编写 ListInactiveSandboxes 测试\n- [ ] 4.10 编写 UpdateSessionLastActivity 测试（Success/NotFound/ZeroTime/EmptyID）\n- [ ] 4.11 编写 Close 测试\n- [ ] 4.12 运行 `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -count=1` 全部通过\n\n**Verification:** 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%（`go test -cover ./pkg/store/...`）；所有测试全绿\n\n---\n\n## T5. 竞态检测与门禁验证\n\n- [ ] 5.1 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/store/...` 无 data race 警告\n- [ ] 5.2 确认无 `log.Printf` 使用（仅允许 `klog`）\n- [ ] 5.3 确认日志中无敏感数据（密码、连接字符串）\n- [ ] 5.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/store/...` 无警告\n- [ ] 5.5 确认 `go build ./pkg/store/...` 编译通过\n\n**Verification:** 以上 5 项全部通过\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1 ──→ T2 ──→ T3 ──→ T4 ──→ T5\n```\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n| # | Criterion | Command |\n|---|-----------|---------|\n| AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n| AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -count=1` |\n| AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/store/...` |\n| AC4 | 覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `go test -cover ./pkg/store/...` |\n| AC5 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n| AC6 | Store 接口签名与 design.md §3.1 一致 | 代码审查 |\n| AC7 | `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` 使用 MGET 批量加载 | 代码审查 |\n| AC8 | `StoreSandbox` 拒绝零 ExpiresAt | `TestValkeyStore_StoreSandbox_ZeroExpiry` 通过 |\n| AC9 | 构造函数返回 error 而非 klog.Fatal | 代码审查 + 单元测试 |\n| AC10 | `STORE_TYPE=valkey` 时 singleton 选择 Valkey 后端 | 代码审查 + 测试 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775836331438,"end":1775836331445}}}}
